[Desktop Entry]
Type=Application
Name=FasdManager
Name[ru]=FasdManager
Name[it]=FasdManager
Name[zh]=FasdManager
Comment=Hybrid file manager with a macOS Finder and GNOME Nautilus interface
Comment[ru]=Гибридный файловый менеджер с интерфейсом macOS Finder и GNOME Nautilus
Comment[it]=File manager ibrido con interfaccia macOS Finder e GNOME Nautilus
Comment[zh]=融合 macOS Finder 与 GNOME Nautilus 界面风格的混合式文件管理器
Exec=fasdmanager %U
Icon=org.fasd.manager
Terminal=false
Categories=System;FileTools;FileManager;GTK;
Keywords=files;file manager;finder;nautilus;dolphin;explorer;
StartupNotify=true
StartupWMClass=org.fasd.manager
